name: CARGO FLIGHTS! TUI Group Boeing 787-9 Dreamliners at Calgary Airport
description:
Thank you to RadarBox for supporting this plane spotting video! Find out more about them at https://www.radarbox.com/?referrer=AlexAviation

Throughout late March and early April 2021, several Boeing 787 Dreamliners belonging to the TUI Group flew into Calgary from Europe, operating a series of cargo charter flights.

After what's been a fairly dry 12 months for YYC spotters, these TUI 787s brought some colour to YYC and some badly-needed international action.

Enjoy these 787s!

FLIGHT INFORMATION
Airline: TUI Airways (TOM/BY) and TUI fly Netherlands (TFL/OR)
Aircraft: Boeing 787-9 and 787-8 Dreamliners (B789/B788)
Flight Number: BY8821 / BY8823 / BY825P / OR7842
Livery: TUI Group "Dreamliner" 
Engines: 2x GEnx-1B
Registration: G-TUIN / G-TUIO / PH-TFM
Route: Manchester (MAN) - Calgary (YYC) - Manchester (MAN) / Brussels (BRU)
Callsign: TOMJET 8821/ 8823 / 825P / ORANGE 7842
Runway used: 35L/ 29 / 17R / 35L
Date filmed: Multiple
